maatoolIsAWebBasedTool: MAA Tool is a web-based tool that supports the design and implementation of multi-actor approaches in the context of sustainable development.
maatoolIsDeveloped: MAA Tool is developed by Social Innolabs, a non-profit foundation that aims to serve as a catalyst between technology and society through the promotion of collaboration among different actors for the development of products that improve the quality of life of citizens.
